data.meta_description:
751 likes, 17 comments - radiolenvie on May 20, 2024: "Happy Birthday to Cher, born Cherilyn Sarkisian on May 20, 1946, in El Centro, California!

Described as embodying female autonomy in a male-dominated industry, she is known for her distinctive contralto singing voice and for having worked in numerous areas of entertainment, as well as adopting a variety of styles and appearances during her five-decade-long career, which has led to her being nicknamed the Goddess of Pop.
#cher #pop #sonnyandcher".
